   "end": "9.520", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.680", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.120", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Anliegen des vorliegenden Gesetzentwurfes ist durchaus nachvollziehbar und auch zu begr\u00fc\u00dfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.280", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zwischen 2015 und 2017 haben sich die Eingangszahlen bei den Verwaltungsgerichten deutlich erh\u00f6ht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.400", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "W\u00e4hrend in den anderen Bereichen die Eing\u00e4nge relativ stabil bei 100\u00a0000 im Jahr liegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.480", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben sie sich bei Asylsachen vervierfacht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.000", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von 50\u00a0000 auf jetzt 200\u00a0000 im Jahr. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.840", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Rund 365\u00a0000\u00a0Asylklagen sind derzeit anh\u00e4ngig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.320", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit den 1\u00a0700\u00a0Verwaltungsrichtern in der ersten Instanz kann man aber nur 200\u00a0000\u00a0F\u00e4lle j\u00e4hrlich erledigen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.080", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Selbst wenn die Zahl der Neuzug\u00e4nge auf das Niveau des Jahres 2015 zur\u00fcckginge, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.840", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was wir derzeit aber nicht absehen k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.200", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "w\u00fcrde der R\u00fcckstand j\u00e4hrlich um nur 50\u00a0000\u00a0F\u00e4lle reduziert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.880", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Ganze ist also ein Projekt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.000", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das uns in jedem Fall noch \u00fcber Jahre begleiten wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.520", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Verwaltungsgerichte wenden derzeit drei Viertel ihrer Energie nur f\u00fcr die Asylverfahren auf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.880", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "obwohl das ein Teilaspekt ihrer Zust\u00e4ndigkeit ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.000", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ganz wichtige Bereiche sind auch Ausbildungsf\u00f6rderung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.600", 
