   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.920", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch mit dem h\u00f6chsten Einsatz und Ver\u00e4nderungen des Prozessrechts wird man das aktuelle Problem nicht l\u00f6sen k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.720", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sprich: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.520", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu z\u00fcgigen Verfahren kommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.520", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die auch unseren rechtsstaatlichen Anforderungen entsprechen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.760", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es sind Ma\u00dfnahmen erforderlich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.120", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Frage ist nur, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.240", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "welche."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.480", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00c4nderungen am Prozessrecht\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.520", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dar\u00fcber kann man diskutieren\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.680", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "werden das Grundproblem der personellen Unterbesetzung nicht beheben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.640", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "400 zus\u00e4tzliche Stellen reichen nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.280", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier m\u00fcssen die L\u00e4nder bei der ersten Instanz noch einmal deutlich nachbessern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.160", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im vorliegenden Gesetzentwurf geht es im Kern darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.160", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in Fragen von grunds\u00e4tzlicher Bedeutung auch die Berufung durch die Verwaltungsgerichte zuzulassen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.120", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Weiterhin sollen Verwaltungsgerichte bei Fragen von grunds\u00e4tzlicher Bedeutung die Beschwerde gegen Beschl\u00fcsse im einstweiligen Rechtsschutz zulassen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.600", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um fall\u00fcbergreifende allgemeine Tatsachenfragen der Entscheidung in h\u00f6chster Instanz zuzuf\u00fchren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.240", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sehen Sie die M\u00f6glichkeit der Revision vor."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.160", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Richtig ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.000", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass obergerichtliche Entscheidungen bei schwierigen und streitigen Fragen nicht nur den Gerichten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.600", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern sicherlich auch dem BAMF Orientierung geben werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.480", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber es ist doch zweifelhaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.280", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob es tats\u00e4chlich zu der gew\u00fcnschten Verfahrensbeschleunigung kommt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.400", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Niemand kann vorhersehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.520", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in wie vielen F\u00e4llen von der M\u00f6glichkeit der Berufung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.960", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Beschwerde und Revision Gebrauch gemacht wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.640", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eines ist doch klar: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.800", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer zus\u00e4tzliche Rechtsmittel einf\u00fchrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.440", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wird zun\u00e4chst einmal erreichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.040", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Verfahren l\u00e4nger dauern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.040", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie in jedem Fall komplizierter werden\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.480", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zumindest vorr\u00fcbergehend\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.560", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
