   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.000", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Entscheidung wird nicht so schnell rechtskr\u00e4ftig werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.920", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Aufenthaltsstatus der Betroffenen wird sich sogar noch verfestigen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.960", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In letzter Instanz k\u00f6nnte das auch zu fehlender Akzeptanz der aktuellen Politik, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "266.360", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
