   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.480", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe gesagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.040", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es ein guter Ansatz ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.240", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber wir m\u00fcssen die Risiken mit dem abw\u00e4gen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "283.520", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was wir m\u00f6glicherweise erreichen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "283.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "286.160", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesregierung pr\u00fcft aktuell, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "286.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "286.960", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
